{"tid":2489014,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】2102號熱帶氣旋 舒力基 SURIGAE（02W）","createTime":"2021-04-14T15:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T02:02:23.000Z","uid":44630,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"efd637f91be369906f0502573d6775f72b02e546","tid":2489014,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋 舒力基</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"x-large\"> 2102號熱帶氣旋 舒力基 SURIGAE（02W）</span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">來源：朝鮮<br />\n意義：一種鷹</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。 <br />\n為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。 <br />\n請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。 <br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span> <br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">部份手機於使用app版時可能無法載入以下圖片，暫時需要按入圖片並選擇在瀏覽器開啟或使用web版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"purple\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_2102.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_2102.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/zoom_2102.png\" /> <br />\n▲香港天文台(HKO) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/2102-00.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/2102-00.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom24l/2102-00.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/202102W.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/SURIGAE.PNG\" /><br />\n▲各機構綜合預測</strong>"},{"pid":"0c25a12a250988fba3ecc6ffd80b75015bb6727c","tid":2489014,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"purple\"><ins>◤颱風追擊必備資訊</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n◆ 香港天文台 (HKO)：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/informtc/tcSmap_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Finformtc%2FtcSmap_uc.htm&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=6cc6c4d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/informtc/tcSmap_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 日本氣象廳 (JMA)：<a href=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jma.go.jp%2Fjp%2Ftyph&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=7b63cc96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh</a><br />\n◆ 中央氣象台 (CMA)：<a href=\"http://www.nmc.gov.cn/publish/typhoon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmc.gov.cn%2Fpublish%2Ftyphoon&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=a1f662df\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nmc.gov.cn/publish/typhoon</a><br />\n◆ 中央氣象局 (CWB)：<a href=\"http://www.cwb.gov.tw/V7/prevent/typhoon/ty.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cwb.gov.tw%2FV7%2Fprevent%2Ftyphoon%2Fty.htm&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f644ce6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cwb.gov.tw/V7/prevent/typhoon/ty.htm</a><br />\n◆ 韓國氣象廳 (KMA)：<a href=\"http://web.kma.go.kr/chn/weather/typoon/typhoon.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.kma.go.kr%2Fchn%2Fweather%2Ftypoon%2Ftyphoon.jsp&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=803d4e88\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.kma.go.kr/chn/weather/typoon/typhoon.jsp</a><br />\n◆ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC)：<a href=\"http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.usno.navy.mil%2FJTWC&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=b1eb6cc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC</a><br />\n◆ 美國海軍實驗中心 (NRL)：<a href=\"http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/TC.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nrlmry.navy.mil%2FTC.html&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=4c99c959\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/TC.html</a><br />\n<br />\n◇ 認識熱帶氣旋：<a href=\"http://j.mp/tc_edu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2Ftc_edu&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=ee27b066\" target=\"_blank\">http://j.mp/tc_edu</a><br />\n◇ 熱帶氣旋實時資料：<a href=\"http://j.mp/tc_realtime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2Ftc_realtime&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=89366d13\" target=\"_blank\">http://j.mp/tc_realtime</a><br />\n◇ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=99fc4ff9\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://bit.ly/2AnFp4H\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://bit.ly/2WnV1h8\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"https://bit.ly/2LltW7T\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pNBL9q\" /> <br />\n▲ 水汽圖<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2a7TpCM\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" /> <br />\n▲ 熱帶系統分佈<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>渦度、風切、輻合輻散及駛流圖的圖片因初學者較難理解已收起，以節省空間及減少讀取之數據量，欲查閲者請自行打開</strong></span></span><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nmxoSz\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pn2N10\" /> <br />\n▲ 渦度<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nHiMVb\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/oJKmvW\" /> <br />\n▲ 垂直風切變<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/od23Nx\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pkPCsA\" /> <br />\n▲ 高空輻散<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/ndaL81\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/noFlPK\" /> <br />\n▲ 低層輻合<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/qjDsUy\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/o4Jzi5\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nUmvwF\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/od7LAQ\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/q73CZx\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/r3N8cc\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/ohj5iY\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nZajhj\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/qOjq3w\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nnWrjt\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/rcX7BC\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/p388ZC\" /> <br />\n▲ 駛流圖 (請按照熱帶氣旋的氣壓參考) </blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/o1uJVb\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/qItfkL\" /> <br />\n▲ 浪高／浪向<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/dmH6HF\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/cA53Zd\" /> <br />\n▲ 海水溫度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2ouh1JP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2ouh1JP.png&h=42d7d586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶氣旋會怎麼走？</strong>"},{"pid":"fe44404e9f03163a85d516d6add5c6db505f8dc7","tid":2489014,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:42:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://m.weather.gov.hk/image/radar_scale.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.weather.gov.hk%2Fimage%2Fradar_scale.jpg&h=087d95fd&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_256_320/rad256_6.jpg\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_128_320/rad128_6.jpg\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_064_320/rad064_6.jpg\" /><br />\n▲ 香港256／128／64公里雷達<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qQj8Xe\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qqyU9G\" /><br />\n▲ 實時天氣照片<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qPKaOw\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qu5ZAb\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2rdU6AS\" /><br />\n▲ 本港分區氣溫／濕度／能見度<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2pSLUlJ\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2rqtOIV\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2sLVc4U\" /><br />\n▲ 本港風向及風速／最高陣風／海平面氣壓</strong>"},{"pid":"2d24f2a90e16b32600a0b6644df748f163f3831a","tid":2489014,"uid":44630,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png&h=fae8adfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png&h=60556b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png&h=85440aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png&h=27f79c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGW（gale warning)－由日本氣象廳發出，意思係24小時內會有熱帶風暴形成，即係估計24小時內命名<br />\nTCFA （tropical cyclone formation alert）－由JTWC發出，指24小時會有熱帶氣旋（包括熱帶低氣壓）生成，即24小時內正式編號升格<br />\nFFS－美國全球預報系統(GFS)的俗稱，諷刺其計算結果如同FF，近年預報準確度有所提升<br />\nCPA TO HK－該風暴與本港之最接近距離<br />\nJTWC BIN C之旅-收集每報JTWC預報報文中的CPA TO HK，事後可以實際CPA TO HK對照作BIN C之用<br />\n馮瑞權－澳門氣象局前局長<br />\n風水權－馮瑞權俗稱<br />\nCCM－天文台新任台長鄭楚明簡稱<br />\n赤的疑惑－高登氣象台台長，連登CDROM<br />\n七長官/7長官-製作氣象台警報gif會員<br />\nRose－製作高登風格天氣警告圖的會員，其作品並不授予連登使用<br />\n楊振權副庭長－Baroclinic於高登的最新名字<br />\n桜の抹茶刺身－連登氣象post負責人1<br />\n道地檸檬綠茶－連登氣象post負責人2<br />\n雪菜肉絲炆米－連登颱風航空交通post負責人<br />\n一個地球人－連登中仔細分析颱風走向及其他高空氣象圖的高質會員，近一年較少上水<br />\n當榴蓮遇上芒果－連登中另一位氣象知識豐富的高質會員<br />\n逝去的不回來/夏天冬天夏天－知名假膠attention seeker<br />\n南珠隻狗－連登中氣象知識亦較豐富的會員<br />\n伊甸園菜肉餃－伊甸園市長在連登的最新名字<br />\nXXXXXX堅豎－土豆在連登的分身，近一年較少上水<br />\nDH-direct hit 本港一百公里內掠過<br />\n中出－風暴中心直接橫過本港<br />\n貓5－cat5 五級颱風的英文簡稱<br />\n五隻貓－同上，有cat1-5<br />\n醉警－酷熱天氣警告誤字<br />\n南海之王－氣象迷對香港天文台的尊稱，指其對南海熱帶氣旋預測表現良好，但只限接近廣東沿岸的南海部份，因此又被稱為南海北部之王<br />\nSTNR－滯留不動<br />\nN0.1－向北移0.1度，/E/S/W（東/南/西）同理<br />\n8中X－天文台指定8個測風站中有X個達標<br />\nlogin－登陸，源於cctvb錯將&Prime;登陸&Prime;打成&Prime;登錄&Prime;<br />\nlogin password－由上引申之術語，意指登陸地<br />\n0號觀望訊號－香港傳媒於熱帶氣旋仍末形成時，已大肆吹奏香港會打風；又或熱帶氣旋已形成，但並非採取接近本港之路徑，傳媒卻仍吹奏有機會打風。此詞用於諷刺傳媒猶如代替天文台發出熱帶氣旋警告訊號<br />\n(香港)暴雨走廊－指大嶼山東北起，經荃青葵，擴展至沙田大埔一段，因西南水汽易受此一帶地型抬升影響較易有暴雨。靈感來自美國「龍捲風走廊」。以下為經典例子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=33884fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e80d38ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為一分鐘風速標準，轉化至十分鐘標準（hko,jma標準）請乘0.93<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nchanho.jpg－副檔名可以改為任意三個不同英文字，為伊甸園市長愛用圖片，即下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c1ebcd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下圖為兩登氣象台提及峴港時愛用cap圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5d8a07b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在洲－「在維多利亞港內的青洲」，天文台以海拔較高且位於廣義維港邊緣的青洲暗示港內達烈風，為天文台搬龍門的代表例子"},{"pid":"a41b99fc4e813d3207937484d47e256f3d397617","tid":2489014,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"有無人有JMA路徑圖link? @JMA控"},{"pid":"a275c44bd5b367f8daf54b935ea569b3e8e955a2","tid":2489014,"uid":332625,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"久違的風po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68afb1d1a08c81ac7cca9db5effbc3f747797e61","tid":2489014,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"已經遠去，如冇意外"},{"pid":"95c6749a5fa4ed6008908d022ab0abbb53e4fef2","tid":2489014,"uid":393962,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"新post LM<br />\n目前沙田仍然有微雨，雷達未能偵測"},{"pid":"df3e57ec05aa45e603fa4744fc20e5d46dbe5fe1","tid":2489014,"uid":393962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"68afb1d1a08c81ac7cca9db5effbc3f747797e61","tid":2489014,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"已經遠去，如冇意外"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"0號觀測信號現正生效<br />\n除非傳媒停止炒作<br />\n否則改發更高信號機會極微"},{"pid":"c41dcf2c0b7c